AMEV Holdings Inc, the New York-basedoperating arm of NV AMEV &lt;AMEV.AS> in The Netherlands andparent company of Security Mutual Finance Corp, said it reacheda definitive agreement to sell Security Mutual to USA FinancialServices Inc.    Security Mutual, based in Decatur, Ala., operates 33 loanoffices in fourh Southeastern states and has 90 mln dlrs inreceivables outstanding.    USA Financial is a subsidiary of Chicago-based UnitedSavings of America. Reuter&#3;